  "response_text": "A bright, solid sky-blue background fills the screen. From the right edge, the end of a Hershey’s chocolate bar wrapper slides into view. The package is glossy dark brown, with a crimped metallic gold-and-silver foil end on the left side and a deep blue shadow cast beneath it. As more of the wrapper appears, large white block letters spell “HERSHEY’S,” with small vertical text reading “SINCE 1894” near the left. Beneath the brand name, smaller white and pale green lettering identifies it as “milk chocolate with whole almonds,” and a small product image with almonds appears toward the right side of the wrapper.\n\nThe left end of the wrapper begins to tear open. The shiny foil and brown paper peel back in jagged, crumpled flaps, revealing the actual milk chocolate bar inside. The chocolate is a warm medium brown with a smooth, glossy surface. As the wrapper pulls farther away, the bar is exposed, showing the word “HERSHEY” embossed in large raised letters across the chocolate.\n\nThe view moves along the chocolate bar to emphasize its surface. Instead of being completely flat, the milk chocolate is rounded and uneven in places, with whole almonds pushing up from underneath like smooth oval bumps. Some almond shapes are more distinct, with shiny highlights and faint ridges visible through the chocolate coating. The bar remains on the clean blue background, its lower edge casting a strong dark blue shadow, making the chocolate look raised above the surface.\n\nThe chocolate continues to glide across the screen, alternating between views of the embossed “HERSHEY” lettering and close views of the almond bumps. The surface appears mostly smooth between the raised almond shapes, with soft reflections across the chocolate.\n\nNear the end, the bar rests diagonally on the blue background, partly inside its opened wrapper. The wrapper is bunched around the right end, with the dark brown Hershey’s packaging and metallic foil folded back around the chocolate. A whole almond and a few small crumbs float or sit just above the exposed end of the bar on the left. Large cream-colored text appears above and to the left of the product, reading “heartwarming the world.” The final image holds on the diagonal chocolate bar, the opened wrapper, the almond pieces, and the large slogan against the bright blue background.",
